### Get books WITH author details
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$expand=author

### Get books WITH genre details
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$expand=genre

### Get books with BOTH author and genre
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$expand=author,genre

### Get an author WITH all their books
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Authors?$expand=books

### Get borrowings with book and member details
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Borrowings?$expand=book,member

### Get members with their borrowings AND the borrowed book
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Members?$expand=borrowings($expand=book)

### Filter books by a specific author
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=author_ID eq 'a1a1a1a1-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa'

### Available books
GET http://localhost:4004/reports/AvailableBooks

### Overdue borrowings
GET http://localhost:4004/reports/OverdueBorrowings

### Book pricing
GET http://localhost:4004/reports/BookPricing

### Member activity
GET http://localhost:4004/reports/MemberActivity?$filter=isActive eq true

### Without $expand
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$select=title,author

### With $expand
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$select=ID,title&$expand=author($select=ID,firstName,lastName)

### Cheapest books first
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=price

### Most expensive books first
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=price desc

### Highest edition books first
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=edition desc

### Alphabetical by title
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=title

### Published date newest to oldest
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=publishedDate desc

### Sort by price descending
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=price desc

### First 2 books
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$top=2

### First 5 books sorted by price
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=price&$top=5

### Page 1
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$top=3&$skip=0

### Page 2
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$top=3&$skip=3

### Page 3
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$top=3&$skip=6

### Top 3 most expensive books
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=price desc&$top=3

### Second page of results, 2 per page
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=title&$top=2&$skip=2

### Navigation Query - Get author of a specific book
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books(1a2b3c4d-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)/author